data.description: Come visit this 3 bedroom/ 2 bath condo in the popular, gated Rolling Hills Condominiums and see what all the fuss is about! This lower level unit is next to a privacy fence, so no neighbors on that side, making it feel a little more private. It has a large, open patio, perfect for letting kids play or just sitting and relaxing outdoors.  Inside, the condo features beautiful, brand new LVP flooring and fresh paint throughout the entire condo - NO CARPET.  The lighting fixtures are new, as well as the blinds and the master bath vanity.  The wood burning fireplace makes a great focal point for the living room, and the HOA has the chimney cleaned once a year. The HOA just replaced the windows 3 years ago, and the community pool has just been renovated this year! The community clubhouse by the pool is a plus for summertime fun. Rolling Hills is close to the mall, restaurants, VSU, the hospital, and much that Valdosta has to offer, and is an easy hop onto I-75.
